HEADWORD: Antipodal
<hw>An*tip"o*dal</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Pertaining to the antipodes; situated on the opposite side of the
globe.</def>⟦br⟧
